<br>
He approaches Giligan and drops two stones on the table.  &quot;Why didn't you tell me these cost nearly 250pp each?&quot; the gnome questions.  <br>
<br>
The master jeweler looks down with a grin and says, &quot;A Fulligrans Soulstone and a Cloudy Stone of Veeshan.  So you finally did it?  Congratulation.&quot;  <br>
<br>
Still beaming Arrington adds, &quot;Yes, Tobon Starpyre finally taught me the third step of a true Wizard.  I now can port to the plane of Hate and Sky.&quot;  <br>
<br>
Hikanur spits beer on the floor.  A VERY uncharacteristic waste of beer for a dwarf.  &quot;The zones where 46th seasoned warriors are newbies?&quot;  he coughs.  <br>
<br>
&quot;Yes&quot; Arrington replies.  &quot;The very same.&quot;  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
